---
title: Kickin’ Sheet Pan Orange BBQ Meatloaves with Cheesy Potato Wedges & Roasted Broccoli
description: Finding yourself in a meatloaf rut? Enter this sweet and savory version. First, we blend ground pork with BBQ seasoning, scallions, and crispy panko breadcrumbs. Next, we form the mixture into mini loaves (so that everyone gets their own!). The pièce de résistance? We swap out the usual ketchup glaze for BBQ sauce that’s laced with smoky chipotle powder and tangy mandarin orange juice. Add sides of cheesy potato wedges and roasted broccoli, and your usual meat-and-spuds dinner is new and improved!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61e85203ffdee97a231cb2dc-9b69b2f4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/kickin-sheet-pan-orange-bbq-meatloaves-61e85203ffdee97a231cb2dc-9942b26b.pdf
